	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.I.D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto demum per nostrum <persName type="auto_name">Burkhardum</persName><note type="misc">vgl. <bibl>Zwa</bibl> XIX/1 121, Anm. 30</note> tuas ad pie memoriae virum <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8418">Myconium</persName> epistolas omnes, quas difficulter ab hęrede tandem extorsi, <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Bullingere</persName> clarissime, eo quod thesauri instar haberet, quicquid a doctis hinc inde viris ad tantum virum scriptum esset.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Galliis</placeName> (quantum ex filii, qui <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378">Lutetiae</placeName> bonis literis navat operam, intelligo) nullum est aut certe simulatur bellum, proditiones tamen vigent, et ne faba in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822">Germanorum</placeName> tandem caput cudatur, verendum est.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6133">Guilielmus Postellus</persName>, qui hactenus frequenti auditorio philosophum et theologum se <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378">Lutetiae</placeName> praestiterat, nunc invidorum malevolentiae cedens clam aufugit; indici centum coronati edicto publico decreti sunt, qui latebras illius detexerit.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Causa nulla alia est, nisi quod acrius in principum et pontificum mores quotidianis huius quadragesimae transactae concionibus invectus fuerit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Accusatores tamen haereseos et seditionis illum insimularunt praetextum alium sibi fingentes.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De rebus <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l850">Austriacis</placeName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l882">Hungaricis</placeName> etc. ex ipso <persName type="citizen_name">Lazio</persName>, viro doctissimo, certior fies.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nos de Caesare nec verbum quidem audimus, de marchionis vero <persName type="citizen_name">Alberti</persName> furioso impetu varia, qui nuper <placeName type="auto_name">Bombergam</placeName> deditione occupasse atque episcopum ingenti pecunia mulctasse fertur.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ego tuis ad me literis scire percupio, quid de evangelio iterum <placeName ref="l257">Constantiae</placeName> praedicando certi habeas.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28">Basileae</placeName> anno 1553 pridie nonas maii, eo videlicet die, quo olim <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l425">Roma</placeName> tertia oppugnatione a Caesarianis militibus capta, <persName type="citizen_name">Albertus</persName>, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l850">Austriae</placeName> dux, rex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2449">Bohemiae</placeName> declaratus, et <persName type="citizen_name">Ioannes Damascenus</persName>, insignis sui temporis theologus, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1148">Constantinopoli</placeName> fatis concessit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">T[uus] <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8406">Lycosthenes</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Vigilantissimo ecclesiae <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurinae</placeName> episcopo d. <persName ref="p495" type="auto_name">Henrico Bullingero</persName>, domino atque amico incomparabili.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigurum</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
